# TruePrice — optional Smart Assist (Gemini) configuration.
#
# Everything works WITHOUT this file: the guided inspection runs on free, private,
# on-device computer vision by default. Smart Assist is a purely optional layer that,
# when a key is present, lets Gemini SUGGEST the variant/condition from a captured photo
# (you still confirm).
#
# To enable it:
#   1. Get a free key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#   2. Copy this file to `.env`  ->  cp .env.example .env
#   3. Paste your key below and restart the server.
#
# NOTE: `.env` is gitignored and must NEVER be committed. Enabling Smart Assist sends
# captured frames to Google — the on-device default sends nothing.

GEMINI_API_KEY=
# Optional: override the model (defaults to gemini-2.5-flash)
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
